  <section class="about">
    <h1 class="about-header">A little bit about me</h1>
    <p class="about-body">A year ago, I made the terrifying decision to change careers.
      I had worked in the city for several years at a management consultancy,
      in a role which had left me feeling empty, exhausted and disilusioned,
      I believed, since we spend the majority of our lives at work, it's important
      to spend this time doing something that we are passionate about.
    </p>
    <p class="about-quote">"The most difficult thing is the decision to act,
      the rest is merely tenacity. The fears are paper tigers.
      You can do anything you decide to do.
      You can act to change and control your life;
      and the procedure, the process is its own reward."
    </p>
    <p class="about-quote-subject">Amelia Earhart</p>
    <p class="about-body">A friend had introduced me to the magical world
      of programming and I was instantly hooked. I knew I was hooked, because my wife had to ask me
      to go sleep at 4am after being glued to my MacBook for the better part of sixteen hours.
      I joined Makers Academy and four months later, I was one step closer to my dream.
    </p>
