<section class="about">
  <h1 class="about-header">And even more...</h1>
  <p class="about-body">
    Whilst in Laos, South-East Asia, I had the amazing opportunity to of teaching English to monks in Laos. I spent two weeks, following their
    daily routine, from waking up at dawn to walk the streets begging for rice, to meditation and chanting at temple. Thier kindness and genorosity
    will stay with me for ever.
  </p>
  <p class="about-body">
    Another incredible experience, was working with underprivildged children in Nepal, Mexico and Peru.
    The photos below are from some of my students from a school in a town called Lubhu, just outside of Kathmandu.
  </p>
  <p class="about-body">
    I have mentioned 'passion' a number of times. This was deliberate. The day I decided to change my career, I decied to change my entire life.
    Start eating healthier, exercise regularly, spend more time with family and friends, read more and most importantly, start each day with the aim of consciously
    making it a great day, not waiting for it to happen.
  </p>
  <p class="about-body">
    Today, 'passion', is what defines me.
  </p>
